parameters: There's a strong-looking monster.... Will you fight it?

It's a monument for defeating a unique monster.... \! The
Platinum Swordsman, would you like to have a rematch? \!

Hey, have you defeated the Unique Boss? It's more of a
challenge, so you don't have to fight it if you don't want
to...

The one on the right, Are, is a type that is faithful to the
basics, so it might be just right as a practice opponent. Do
you need any advice?

First, let's aim for weakening! Leave it to Vita around here
and rest assured! Make sure to lower it by two stages
properly!!

And let's use Lunaroa's Secret Technique too! It shines the
most against strong opponents. With 4 actions, we can
destroy everything...!!

Laura will maintain her enhancement with Radiant Sword while
attacking, providing support and healing! I also recommend
using Cheerful Ail!
That's all!! Everyone, I pray for your success...!!

H-Hmm? Not bad, huh? From my perspective, you still have a
long way to go, but would you like me to show you a little?
Just a little bit, okay?

Isn't it funny when Vita's Counter keeps coming out in
succession? I laughed the first time I saw it.
